## Commands to Run

### Rebuild the container (required — new dependencies)
```bash
docker compose up --build -d backend
```

### Run Phase 2 tests first (required — seeds test_repo into ChromaDB)
```bash
docker exec -it coderag-project-backend-1 python tests/test_phase2.py
```

### Run Phase 3 tests
```bash
docker exec -it coderag-project-backend-1 python tests/test_phase3.py
```

