## Troubleshooting

| Symptom | Likely cause | Fix |
|---------|-------------|-----|
| Test 5 returns `"No results retrieved"` | `test_repo` not in ChromaDB | Run Phase 2 tests first |
| `ModuleNotFoundError: langgraph` | Container not rebuilt | `docker compose up --build -d backend` |
| `ImportError: cannot import name 'StateGraph'` | Wrong langgraph version | Check `requirements.txt` has `langgraph==0.1.5` |
| Confidence is always low | FLAN-T5 hypothesis doesn't overlap with code keywords | Expected — the agent will loop up to 3 times then respond anyway |
